messageBody:
Hello,
I am looking for some Junit test classes for a research experiment I am doing for my thesis. I will be grateful to anyone who can provide me with source code (buggy versions are more than welcome) and test cases.
I promise the code won't be published or distributed. I just need it to collect some data for my thesis.
Thank you for your help.
 
Layla
